an truncation methods. We also\ndiscuss some subtleties related to the physical interpretation of the mass gap\nand provide evidence that the kink mass can be obtained by analytic\ncontinuation from the unbroken to the broken phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jan 2019 19:02:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Apr 2019 09:41:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-05"}
