cted sideband emission in HOIPs, clarify discrepancies in\nprevious literature, and generally challenge the paradigm of ED-dominated\nlight-matter interactions in novel optoelectronic materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jan 2019 05:09:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Apr 2019 15:39:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-16"}
