, QCD NNLO and EW NLO corrections in di-lepton final states are\nnot expected to change the conclusions of this study. New results pertaining to\nthe production of two opposite sign different flavour charged leptons with a\nfull jet veto further confirm the presence of anomalies in similar corners of\nthe leptonic phase-space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jan 2019 14:13:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 May 2019 09:14:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2019 13:08:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-18"}
