P combinations for 80 of\nthe 108 HSPs, and future work exists for the testing of this method of\nprediction using real patient data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jan 2019 07:25:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Feb 2019 09:03:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-06"}
